Detection of dislocation motion in atomistic\par
simulations of nanocrystalline materials\par
                    Noya Dimanstein Firman1, Eliyahu Zvi Engelberg2,\u8727?\u59865?\par
                    and Yinon Ashkenazy1,\u8727?\u59865?\par
